See 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDE4B45FFABFFCBFE808115FDE04138" author="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D." box="[328,623,1333,1360]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472" pagination="425 - 442" refId="ref37037" refString="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D. (2019 b) Taxonomy of littoral Melanella (Gastropoda: Eulimidae) from Brazil, with comments on the Eulima species described by Verrill and Bush (1900). Marine Biodiversity, 49 (1), 425 - 442. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12526 - 017 - 0825 - x" type="journal article" year="2019">Souza &amp; Pimenta (2019b)</bibRefCitation>
